snippet.title: 「Fate/stay night REMASTERED」Nintendo Switch™/ Steam® Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Seek the root of the Fate franchise. Return to where it all began.

Fate/stay night REMASTERED coming soon in 2024.
*This title is a remaster of the original PlayStation Vita title "Fate/stay night Réalta Nua" and is available for the first time in English and Simplified Chinese
